description: City Gripe allows users to complain to Alexa about various things in there life including their love life, commute, or the weather. Using Department of Commerce open data, Alexa will either try and suggest somewhere the user could move or will tell the user of an ever worse of county. Winner of "Best use of Commerce Data" at the U.S. Department of Commerce Open Data Alexa Hackathon.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, tell City Gripe I'm sick of my commute because it is too long.
I absolutely can't stand my relationship.
name: City Gripe
shortDescription: Welcome to City Gripe where you can complain to Alexa, about your love life, commute, or the weather.
